Class DfpVersion

java.lang.Object
  com.google.api.ads.dfp.lib.DfpVersion

public abstract class DfpVersion
extends java.lang.Object

For each active version of the DoubleClick For Publishers API, there should exist a sub-class which implements the abstract class.
